snippet.title: Snaketroidvania - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Snaketroidvania is the game I made for Ludum Dare #47.

The protagonist of Snake doesn't really want to snake anymore! He is completely fed up with it, eating apples over and over again. Help him bust out of that dumb game.

Play only or download at:
https://anttihaavikko.itch.io/snaketroidvania
